    <title><![CDATA[【为他准备的谋杀】敢不敢大点儿声]]></title>
    <publishTime>1378192003601</publishTime>
    <type>Text</type>
    <permalink>1a7a1d_8862d3</permalink>
    <tag>读后感,蒋峰,悬疑,硬派,欧阳楠,陈洁</tag>
    <ip>113.108.133.46</ip>
